<body>
	
<header>
	In what order do you think the candidate should perform these tasks after being given the discussion topic? Choose the right order.
</header>
	
<section id="body">
	<img class="rightFloat" src="../Media/LC_SP_004.JPG" mode="1" id="1001"  /><p align="left"><b>In Part 2 of the IELTS Speaking Module you will be given a topic, time to think and make notes, then one to two minutes to talk.</b>Use your time to:</p><ol><li>be clear about instructions</li><li>get your ideas in a logical order</li><li>have enough materials to speak until the examiner stops you</li></ol><p align="left"><b>In what order should you perform these tasks in Part 2 of the Speaking Module?</b><g id="1">A.  Think Speak Write Read</g><g id="2">B.  Think Read Speak Write</g><g id="3">C.  Write Read Speak Think</g><g id="4">D.  Write Speak Read Think</g><g id="5">E.  Read Write Think Speak</g><g id="6">F.  Read Think Write Speak</g><g id="7">G.  Speak Think Read Write</g><g id="8">H.  Speak Write Think Read</g></p>
</section>
<section id="fb1">
	<p align="left">It would be a good idea to find out what you have to do first.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb2">
	<p align="left">It would be difficult to know what to think about.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb3">
	<p align="left">It would be difficult to know what to write.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb4">
	<p align="left">It might be a good idea to find out what you have to do first.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb5">
	<p align="left">It is a better idea to think before you write anything down.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb7">
	<p align="left">Speaking is the last thing you should do.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb8">
